Package es.uniovi.reflection.weavej.weaver.java7

Classes necessary to instrument applications and transform application classes at load time when using java7.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASMClassVisitorJava7
    Subclass of org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor to transform classes at load time when Java 7 is used.
    ASMInnerConstructorVisitorJava7
    Subclass of ASMConstructorVisitor to transform specific class constructors in load time when Java 7 is used.
    ASMMethodVisitorJava7
    Subclass of ASMMethodVisitor to transform class methods in load time when Java 7 is used.
    PackageGroupTransformerJava7
    Subclass of PackageGroupTransformer which employs a different specific class visitor to use with Java 7.

Package es.uniovi.reflection.weavej.weaver.java7 Description

Classes necessary to instrument applications and transform application classes at load time when using java7. One of the main differences with Java 8 is that constructor joinpoints are not supported here.
Version:
1.1.0
Author:
Oscar Rodriguez-Prieto Date: 2017/07/11
